Microcontroller

  • ATmega164/324/644 in 40pin P-DIP package (atmega164-644.sym)
  • ATtiny13 DIP8 or SO8 package (attiny13.sym)
  • ATtiny24/44/84 DIP14 or SO14 package (attiny24.sym)

DC Voltage Sources

  • LM2623: DC/DC Boost Converter (lm2623mm.sym)
  • LP2950: LDO Voltage Regulator (lp2950.sym)
  • LT1946: DC/DC Boost Converter (lt1946.sym)
  • MAX17552: DC/DC Low Current Buck Converter (MAX17552.sym)
  • MIC5295: LDO Voltage Regulator (mic5295.sym)

Connectors

  • Terminal Block - 2 pin, derived from Ales Hvezda's symbol, just modified footprint (tb2p200.sym)
  • Terminal Block - 3 pin, derived from Ales Hvezda's symbol, just modified footprint (tb3p200.sym)
  • Terminal Block - 2 pin, derived from Ales Hvezda's symbol, just modified footprint (tb2p3_5mm.sym)
  • Terminal Block - 3 pin, derived from Ales Hvezda's symbol, just modified footprint (tb3p3_5mm.sym)

Other

  • BSS 123: N-channel MOSFET in SOT-23 package (bss123.sym)
  • BSS 84P: P-channel MOSFET in SOT-23 package (bss84p.sym)
  • BTS4140N: Smart High-Side Power Switch (bts4140n.sym)
  • L9637D: K/L-line Bus Driver, no GND and Vcc pins (L9637D.sym)
  • L9637D: K/L-line Bus Driver, includes GND and Vcc pins (L9637D_allpins.sym)
  • MTS62C19A: Dual Full-Bridge Motor Driver (mts62c19a.sym)
  • Potentiometer, copy of gEDA's "resistor-variable-2", just with assigned footprint for Piher 10mm (poti_10mm.sym)
  • Generic Schottky Diode, with cathode at pin 1 (schottky-3.sym)
  • Inverted Schmitt Trigger, single slot in SOT353 or SOT25 package (74LVC1G17.sym)
  • SN65176B/SN75176B: RS-485/422 bus transceiver (SNx5176B.sym)
